metadata.name: Leap of Faith
metadata.description:
The ultimate question of life, the universe and everything “ Why? ”
	
I earned a ridiculous amount of bonus during the financial crisis in 2008, 
not even breaking a sweat.

" Why Me ?"
“ How did I get it ? ”  
“ Did I deserve this ? ”
	
Instead of staying in my comfort zone and questioning the irony of being successful, 
I made my way towards the unknown and searched for the answer.

Jeff decided to have his gap year in South America. He was 32 year old.
